viewData.name: Lashes Lifting Silicone Shields Large 10pcs
viewData.short_description: Large Shields are great option for those with long natural lashes, and for clients seeking a subtler lash lift, but still a measurable difference in the lash look, resulting with more natural eye look.
viewData.long_description: Phi silicone shields come in three sizes in Small, Medium or Large, providing the clients a multiple option of potential looks that could be created, considering the length of their natural lashes and their preference and expectations of the final look from the lifting procedure. The smaller the shield used the greater and more dramatic the lift is to be achieved. The shields come in white color, providing your work precision even to the smallest details.
